ElectricityStats
public class SurplusReport
extends EquilibriumReport

A report that calculates the actual surplus of buyers and sellers in the auction verses the theoretical surplus when trades occur at the equilibrium price. Note that this report assumes that the equilibrium price is constant. To calculate theoretical surplus with dynamic supply and demand you should configure a DynamicSurplusReport.
